headline: Is Intel Corp Stock a Buy?
summary: Intel stock has sharply lagged its sector, slumping 32% over the past year.  The past few years have been difficult -- to say the least -- for Intel (NASDAQ: INTC).  Competitors like Nvidia have seen their share prices balloon thanks to the rapid rise of AI technologies.
